gov.va.med.srcalc.vista

Enum RemoteProcedure

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RemoteProcedure>
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.vista.RemoteProcedure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RemoteProcedure>

    public enum RemoteProcedure
extends java.lang.Enum<RemoteProcedure>
    Enumerates all VistA Remote Procedures which this application uses. Each enumeration constant is the name of a VistA Remote Procedure with spaces replaced by underscores.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      GMV_EXTRACT_REC
      Returns a vital from the given patient with the specified date range.
      GMV_LATEST_VM
      Returns the most recent vitals on the patient.
      SR_ASRC_ACTIVE_MEDS
      Returns all active VA and non-VA medications for the patient.
      SR_ASRC_ADL_NOTES
      Returns all nursing notes with the "NURSING ADMISSION EVALUATION NOTE" title.
      SR_ASRC_DNR_NOTES
      Returns any nursing notes for the specified patient, that contain the specified substring.
      SR_ASRC_GET_PATIENT
      Returns information about the given patient.
      SR_ASRC_HEALTH_FACTORS
      Returns any of the patient's health factors in the last year.
      SR_ASRC_LAB_RESULTS
      Returns the most recent result for the given lab name possibilities.
      SR_ASRC_PERSON_CLASSES
      Returns Person Classes for the current user.
      SR_ASRC_RISK_SAVE
      Saves a Risk Calculation as discrete data to VistA Surgery.
      SR_ASRC_SAVE_PROGRESS_NOTE
      Submits a completed calculation as a note on the patient's records.
      XUS_GET_USER_INFO
      Returns information about the current user.
      XUS_KAAJEE_GET_USER_VIA_PROXY
      Returns information about the user associated with the given CCOW token.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String BAD_TOKEN_DUZ
      XUS_KAAJEE_GET_USER_VIA_PROXY returns this DUZ if the token was invalid (or associated with a different client IP).

      VistA returns this string if SR_ASRC_RISK_SAVE succeeds.
      static java.lang.String VALID_SIGNATURE_RETURN
      VistA returns this string if SR_ASRC_SAVE_PROGRESS_NOTE succeeds.

      • XUS_KAAJEE_GET_USER_VIA_PROXY

        public static final RemoteProcedure XUS_KAAJEE_GET_USER_VIA_PROXY

        Returns information about the user associated with the given CCOW token.

        See the OSEHRA documentation for parameter and return value documentation. Note that the CCOW token parameter must actually be encrypt("~~TOK~~" + token).

        See Also:
        VistaAuthenticator.authenticateViaCcowToken(String, String)
